                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="info-text-left">Auto Buy Shop For Count Quick Change</td>
                        <td class="info-text-right">: Screenshot hasil pencarian <code class="info-text-highlight">Quick Change</code> saat mode <code class="info-text-highlight">Count Quick Change</code> aktif.</td>
                    </tr>
