                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="info-text-left">Ctrl + F Then L</td>
                        <td class="info-text-right">: <code class="info-text-highlight">Browse file</code> for <code class="info-text-highlight">Log</code></td>
                    </tr>
