                        <td class="info-text-right">: Tekan <code class="info-text-highlight">Enter</code> untuk simpan <code class="info-text-highlight">Weapon</code> & tekan <code class="info-text-highlight">Ctrl + Enter</code> untuk <code class="info-text-highlight">Item</code> (max 20 each).</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="info-text-left">Check Items</td>
                        <td class="info-text-right">: Melihat list <code class="info-text-highlight">weapon/item</code> yang di <code class="info-text-highlight">Simpan</code>.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="info-text-left">Tombol "&#215"</td>
                        <td class="info-text-right">: Hapus list <code class="info-text-highlight">weapon/list</code>.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="info-text-left">"&#9650" & "&#9660"</td>
                        <td class="info-text-right">: Pindahkan urutan <code class="info-text-highlight">list</code> menjadi ke <code class="info-text-highlight">atas</code> atau <code class="info-text-highlight">bawah</code>.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="info-text-left">Delete All</td>
                        <td class="info-text-right">: Hapus semua <code class="info-text-highlight">weapon</code> & <code class="info-text-highlight">item</code> list.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="info-text-left">Auto Buy Shop Path</td>
                        <td class="info-text-right">: Lokasi simpan <code class="info-text-highlight">screenshot</code> (default: C:\Script - TDA\GB Auto Buy Shop - TDA\Auto Buy Shop).</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="info-text-left">Watermark, Room Title, Room Password</td>
                        <td class="info-text-right">: Bebas diisi sesuai <code class="info-text-highlight">kebutuhan</code>, <code class="info-text-highlight">kosongkan</code> jika tidak ingin digunakan.</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <div style="height: 33px;"></div>
            <div style="float:left; margin-left: 10px;">
                <button title="F1" onclick="StartExeScript()">Run Script</button>
            </div>
            <div style="float:right; margin-right: 10px;">
                <button title="Escape/Esc" class="btn-danger" onclick="HideInformation()">Back</button>
            </div>
            <div style="width: 100%; margin: 0; margin-top: 45px; margin-bottom: -7px;">
                <a style="float: left;" class="header whatsapp" href="#" onclick="OpenLink('https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=6289528513371')">Whatsapp: 0895-2851-3371</a>
                <a class="header facebook" href="#" onclick="OpenLink('https://www.facebook.com/topupdisiniaja?rdid=l5sEgiU3Eb6Gkn1O&share_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshare%2F14eRyBmzCTC%2F#')">Facebook: Abdullah Khareem</a>
                <a style="float: right;" class="header instagram" href="#" onclick="OpenLink('https://www.instagram.com/topup_disini_aja')">Instagram: topup_disini_aja</a>
            </div>
